  "body": "### Description\r\nOne of the ancestors of `ERC20PresetFixedSupply` is `ERC20`, which contains:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/ee149877212acf5564921244b3cdaa7266a372fe/contracts/token/ERC20/ERC20.sol#L243-L262\r\n\r\nThis function is also available in `ERC20PresetFixedSupply`.\r\n\r\n### Recommendation\r\nRename `ERC20PresetFixedSupply` to `ERC20PresetInitialSupply`. Alternatively, consider overriding the function `_mint` and replacing \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/ee149877212acf5564921244b3cdaa7266a372fe/contracts/token/ERC777/presets/ERC777PresetFixedSupply.sol#L28\r\n\r\nwith `ERC20.mint`.",
